{"tid":763344,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"過左磨合期相處得好開心，你問我答","createTime":"2018-08-01T04:47:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T17:23:39.000Z","uid":154492,"like":58,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"7c2b1c88a7c5ce88f12ede8371645b6c4aaee875","tid":763344,"uid":154492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:47:30.000Z","msg":"睇下幫唔幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一開始其實我好抗拒同女朋友溝通自己想法/不滿<br />\n因為驚佢聽完唔鐘意 發脾氣<br />\n後尾女朋友提出認真坐低一齊傾<br />\n發現其實好多野女朋友都唔知我點諗<br />\n唔好以為對方係你肚入面條蟲 講左出黎 大家先知對方想法<br />\n<br />\n一人讓一步<br />\n有啲野原來係我做得唔夠<br />\n有啲野係女朋友需要改<br />\n慢慢越來越了解對方<br />\n依家好少嘈 就算有 冷靜左我地都會即刻解決<br />\n<br />\n磨合期間係需要多啲耐性 愛 同坦承<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5b98198215bbe849e7be066516537c09f871b9","tid":763344,"uid":114337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:51:30.000Z","msg":"講撚完咪又係咁 相處得唔開心 拍乜野拖姐 分手啦 <br />\n拍拖好撚攰呀"},{"pid":"6e1ff6083f2b5bf4934b99d07ce7a719e9df246e","tid":763344,"uid":154492,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"6c5b98198215bbe849e7be066516537c09f871b9","tid":763344,"uid":114337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:51:30.000Z","msg":"講撚完咪又係咁 相處得唔開心 拍乜野拖姐 分手啦 <br />\n拍拖好撚攰呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:55:40.000Z","msg":"磨合係雙方既 如果對方冇意咁做<br />\n巴打要考慮下仲適唔適合啦<br />\n對方係咪性格比較唔成熟?"},{"pid":"051f00d25d343d6166776b89abcfc6a398acac76","tid":763344,"uid":154492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T05:05:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c0babdc69dd7009d41db6bacc2b3be4cec7a79","tid":763344,"uid":178896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6c5b98198215bbe849e7be066516537c09f871b9","tid":763344,"uid":114337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:51:30.000Z","msg":"講撚完咪又係咁 相處得唔開心 拍乜野拖姐 分手啦 <br />\n拍拖好撚攰呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T05:06:43.000Z","msg":"小學生發脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515d04d079e6959288f07df7ee883bd2f2549f2e","tid":763344,"uid":187967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T05:10:17.000Z","msg":"最勁果次係因咩事嘈"},{"pid":"543b9248a53c736dc44f440e876993c6d87108a1","tid":763344,"uid":154492,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"515d04d079e6959288f07df7ee883bd2f2549f2e","tid":763344,"uid":187967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T05:10:17.000Z","msg":"最勁果次係因咩事嘈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T05:19:18.000Z","msg":"覺得我唔重視佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為有一排佢成日因小事嘈我<br />\n我覺得有啲煩躁 就少左搵佢<br />\n我唔係唔愛佢 只係想搵少啲希望就可以少啲嘈<br />\n但喺佢眼中就覺得我唔愛佢 唔理佢 唔解決問題<br />\n依一次亦係佢決心要我坐低同佢傾<br />\n溝通返同佢講我以為唔理就可以解決問題<br />\n而佢就認為如果係咁 問題就越積越多<br />\n咁我地互相講返大家想法感受 理解左對方就冇事啦<br />\n<br />\n其餘都係佢呷下醋咁 女仔正常都會呷醋既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n哄兩哄 讚下佢幾好就無事啦<br />\n最忌係唔理佢 女人都係想人讚下佢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ec81410cb7449124152070b9d6286179100996","tid":763344,"uid":154492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T05:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d767c63c39ae69db5934046c19f0c25930fe399","tid":763344,"uid":19948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T05:35:36.000Z","msg":"一齊幾耐"},{"pid":"d23ecb14b6d734a311285765bf5fabbcdc3a2912","tid":763344,"uid":197545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d767c63c39ae69db5934046c19f0c25930fe399","tid":763344,"uid":19948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T05:35:36.000Z","msg":"一齊幾耐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T05:40:33.000Z","msg":"重點"},{"pid":"536ef09fc27bdadc9ee5132ed0c99f876b98dc09","tid":763344,"uid":77571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco